1. Start MongoDB Replica Set
Open PowerShell as administrator:

& "C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Server\8.0\bin\mongod.exe" --dbpath "C:\data\db" --replSet rs0

new terminal :
mongosh
rs.initate();
rs.status();

2. Start Backend Server
Open new terminal:

cd server
npm install
npm run dev

3. Start Frontend
Open another terminal:

cd client
npm install
npm run dev